      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know there are hotlines and stuff but that doesnt change the fact that the pain is still there. it doesnt make the fire in my nerves stop. it just feels like i'm being forced to endure something that's fundamentally cruel. sometimes i just sit here thinking about how much easier it would be if the world just... stopped for me. if there was just peace and nothingness. it feels more like a mercy than a tragedy at this point.",
